---
title: Coconut-Crusted Chicken Fingers with Roasted Green Beans and Fries
description: The secret to tender, juicy, and flavorful chicken fingers? Breading. A crispy panko and slightly sweet coconut one, to be exact. To round out this dish, our chefs added golden potatoes and crispy roasted green beans—two sides that are super simple and easy to prepare.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/coconut-crusted-chicken-fingers-16d2b8bd.jpg
